%20of%20Republicans%20supported%20Trump%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Felection%2F2020%2Fexit-polls%2Fpresident%2Fmichigan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20CNN%20exit%20polling%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20also%20leads%20Trump%2044%25-37%25%20among%20independent%20and%20unaffiliated%20voters%2C%20a%20critical%20bloc%20that%20in%202020%20gave%20him%20strong%20margins%20in%20suburban%20Detroit%20and%20helped%20him%20win%20Kent%20County%2C%20home%20to%20Grand%20Rapids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20offers%20some%20bright%20news%20for%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20sought%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20blue-collar%2C%20working-class%20votes%20who%20often%20play%20the%20decisive%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20outcome%20of%20statewide%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Trump%20narrowly%20won%20Michigan%20over%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20a%20huge%20blow%20to%20Democrats%20as%20the%20party's%20presidential%20nominees%20had%20carried%20the%20state%20in%20every%20election%20from%201992%20to%202012.%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2020-vs-2016-electoral-college-maps-trump-biden-clinton-president-2020-11%5C%22%3Eflipped%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20back%20into%20the%20Democratic%20column%20in%202020%2C%20winning%20by%20roughly%203%25%20over%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20largely%20been%20a%20bright%20spot%20for%20the%20party%20since%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Democrats%20swept%20the%20state%20up%20and%20down%20the%20ballot%2C%20with%20Gov.%20Gretchen%20Whitmer%2C%20state%20Attorney%20General%20Dana%20Nessel%2C%20and%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Jocelyn%20Benson%20all%20winning%20reelection%2C%20while%20the%20party%20also%20captured%20full%20control%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%20With%20the%20current%20Democratic%20stranglehold%20over%20state%20politics%20in%20Lansing%2C%20they're%20looking%20to%202024%2C%20when%20Biden%20will%20be%20on%20the%20ballot%20and%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20to%20defend%20the%20Senate%20seat%20being%20vacated%20by%20retiring%20Sen.%20Debbie%20Stabenow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Democrats%20are%20experiencing%20some%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Auto%20Workers%20union%20is%20on%20strike%20against%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Three%26quot%3B%20automakers%20%E2%80%94%20Ford%2C%20General%20Motors%2C%20and%20Stellantis%20%E2%80%94%20after%20worker%20contracts%20expired%20late%20Thursday.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20only%20three%20plants%20(a%20Ford%20factory%20in%20Wayne%2C%20Michigan%3B%20a%20GM%20assembly%20plant%20in%20Wentzville%2C%20Missouri%3B%20and%20a%20Stellantis%20Jeep%20plant%20in%20Toledo%2C%20Ohio)%20have%20workers%20who%20have%20gone%20on%20strike%20as%20the%20union%20continues%20to%20push%20company%20leaders%20for%20higher%20wages%20and%20stronger%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20pro-union%20president%20in%20American%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20Friday%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20union%20workers%20and%20called%20on%20the%20companies%20to%20share%20their%20profits%20with%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20wants%20to%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20during%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20respect%20workers'%20right%20to%20use%20their%20options%20under%20the%20collective%20bargaining%20system%2C%20and%20I%20understand%20the%20workers'%20frustration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20hurt%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20region%20where%20Biden%20has%20sought%20to%20highlight%20his%20work%20on%20the%20issue.%20The%20president%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F09%2F14%2Fjoe-biden-speech-attacks-trump-maganomics%2F70854205007%2F%5C%22%3Estruggled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20polling%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20voter%20sentiments%20on%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20he%20has%20aggressively%20pitched%20his%20economic%20message%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20on%20Friday%20dispatched%20acting%20Labor%20secretary%20Julie%20Su%20and%20White%20House%20economic%20advisor%20Gene%20Sperling%20%26quot%3Bto%20offer%20their%20full%20support%20for%20the%20parties%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20contract%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusquehanna%20Polling%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20polled%20700%20registered%20Michigan%20voters%20from%20September%207%20through%20September%2012%3B%20the%20survey%20had%20a%20margin%20of%20error%20of%20plus%20or%20minus%203.7%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-leads-trump-desantis-michigan-2024-presidential-poll-auto-strike-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694879153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6505cac4f05aa00019bda2ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-leads-trump-desantis-michigan-2024-presidential-poll-auto-strike-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20Auto%20Workers%20union%20is%20now%20on%20strike%20against%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Three%26quot%3B%20automakers%2C%20which%20has%20created%20uncertainty%20for%20Biden's%20economic%20message.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-leads-trump-desantis-michigan-2024-presidential-poll-auto-strike-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJoe%20Biden%20Not%20Too%20Old%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20On%20America's%20Oldest%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%2C%20America's%20oldest%20president%2C%20received%20support%20from%20an%20unexpected%20ally%20over%20his%20age%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20Democrat%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20too%20old%26quot%3B%20to%20seek%20a%20second%20term%2C%20while%20quickly%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20incompetent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president's%20comments%2C%20made%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20aired%20Sunday%2C%20come%20as%20America%20faces%20a%20profound%20debate%20over%20the%20ageing%20of%20its%20political%20class%2C%20a%20major%20factor%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20--%20when%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20be%20just%20shy%20of%2082%20and%20Trump%20himself%2078.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolls%20show%20that%20while%20the%20age%20gap%20between%20the%20two%20men%20is%20small%2C%20Americans%20worry%20more%20about%20President%20Biden's%20age%2C%20with%20one%20survey%20finding%20that%20three%20in%20four%20people%20doubt%20his%20ability%20to%20last%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Trump%20ended%20his%20own%20term%20in%20office%20as%20the%20second-oldest%20president%20ever%20(Ronald%20Reagan%20was%2077%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20term)%20presents%20the%20real%20estate%20magnate%20with%20a%20challenge%2C%20however%2C%20in%20repeatedly%20portraying%20Biden%20as%20too%20%26quot%3Bsleepy%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20the%20Republican%2C%20who%20would%20be%2082%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20second%20term%2C%20from%20trying%20to%20thread%20that%20needle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20greatest%20world%20leaders%20have%20been%20in%20their%2080s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NBC.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20anywhere%20very%20near%2080%2C%20by%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20Biden's%20not%20too%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Donald%20Trump%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20he's%20incompetent%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20bigger%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%2C%20who%20overcame%20a%20stuttering%20problem%20as%20a%20youth%2C%20has%20often%20been%20mocked%20for%20his%20verbal%20stumbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20remains%20trim%2C%20physically%20active%2C%20does%20not%20drink%20and%20is%20often%20seen%20riding%20his%20bicycle%20during%20weekends%20at%20his%20Delaware%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20say%20he%20also%20fares%20well%20on%20the%20competency%20front%2C%20having%20overseen%20the%20passage%20of%20major%20legislation%2C%20including%20a%20massive%20infrastructure%20bill%2C%20the%20largest%20gun-safety%20bill%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20the%20Build%20Back%20Better%20social%20spending%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20has%20also%20been%20active%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20Indeed%2C%20during%20his%20just-ended%20trip%20to%20Vietnam%20--%20which%20analysts%20say%20was%20staged%20partly%20to%20highlight%20his%20vigour%20--%20that%20country's%2079-year-old%20Communist%20leader%20smilingly%20complimented%20Biden%20on%20his%20relative%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20gotten%20mostly%20positive%20marks%20during%20annual%20physicals%20--%20though%20he%20has%20been%20classed%20as%20overweight%20and%20does%20no%20exercise%20other%20than%20golf.%20Like%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20he%20does%20not%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20too%2C%20has%20had%20his%20share%20of%20bizarre%20verbal%20moments%2C%20mangled%20pronunciations%20and%20physical%20stumbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20NBC%20interview%20he%20said%20his%20own%20age%20does%20not%20concern%20him%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20parents%20had%20long%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20genetically%2C%20that's%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20insistence%20on%20his%20own%20competency%20was%20ridiculed%20during%20the%202020%20presidential%20campaign%20when%20Trump%20said%20he%20had%20scored%20an%20%26quot%3Bamazing%26quot%3B%20result%20on%20what%20he%20said%20was%20a%20test%20of%20mental%20acuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20had%20to%20remember%2C%20in%2