E%3Cp%3EThree%20officers%2C%20Colonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%20and%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20of%20the%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20and%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20Himayun%20Bhat%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20action%2C%20a%20soldier%20is%20missing%20and%20at%20least%20two%20more%20personnel%20have%20been%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20are%20hiding%20in%20a%20cave%20atop%20a%20hill%20in%20the%20Gadul%20forests%20of%20Kokernag%2C%20which%20affords%20them%20protection%20as%20well%20as%20complete%20visibility%20of%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20joint%20Army%20and%20police%20team%20that%20has%20surrounded%20them.%20The%20narrow%20path%20leading%20to%20the%20cave%2C%20which%20offers%20no%20cover%20and%20has%20a%20sheer%20drop%20on%20one%20side%2C%20is%20what%20had%20cost%20the%20three%20personnel%20their%20lives%20as%20the%20team%20began%20their%20first%20offensive%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%2C%20rocket%20launchers%20and%20mortar%20shells%20have%20all%20been%20used%2C%20but%20the%20forces%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20domination%20of%20the%20area%20yet.%20Officials%20say%20they%20are%20confident%20of%20neutralising%20the%20terrorists%20at%20the%20earliest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20the%20establishment%20worried%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20this%20is%20one%20of%20three%20encounters%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20five%20days%20and%20comes%20amid%20an%20uptick%20in%20terrorist%20activity%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20covers%20the%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts.%20Former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20SP%20Vaid%20said%20the%20Anantnag%20encounter%20points%20to%20yet%20another%20change%20in%20strategy%20by%20terrorists%20and%20their%20backers%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETough%20Terrain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHighly%20placed%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20forces%20first%20got%20intelligence%20about%20terrorists%20hiding%20in%20the%20Gadul%20forests%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20and%2C%20on%20learning%20that%20they%20were%20atop%20a%20hill%2C%20a%20decision%20to%20attack%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20path%20the%20forces%20have%20to%20take%20to%20get%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill%20is%20quite%20challenging.%20It%20is%20very%20narrow%20and%20there%20are%20mountains%20and%20a%20dense%20forest%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20deep%20ditch%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20personnel%20began%20the%20ascent%20in%20the%20night%2C%20and%20the%20darkness%20made%20it%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20forces%20ascend%2C%20the%20terrorists%20began%20firing%20at%20the%20personnel%2C%20who%20found%20themselves%20cornered.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20three%20officers%20were%20injured%2C%20but%20the%20limited%20options%20for%20extraction%20meant%20that%20they%20could%20not%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20until%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWell-Stocked%2C%20Well-Trained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20the%20terrorists%20have%20adequate%20stocks%20of%20arms%2C%20ammunition%20and%20even%20food%2C%20which%20is%20evidenced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20managed%20to%20hold%20out%20for%20nearly%2090%20hours.%20They%20said%20the%20number%20of%20terrorists%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20more%20than%20the%20two-three%20that%20is%20being%20mentioned%20in%20most%20reports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20recruit%2C%20Uzair%20Khan%2C%20is%20among%20the%20terrorists%20holed%20up%20in%20the%20cave.%20He%20is%20believed%20to%20know%20the%20area%20very%20well%20and%20the%20terrorists%20are%20benefiting%20from%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOrdinary%20terrorists%20cannot%20stretch%20an%20encounter%20for%20so%20long.%20They%20are%20very%20well-trained%20and%20have%20good%20weapons.%20It%20is%20also%20possible%20that%20an%20informer%20may%20have%20double-crossed%20the%20forces%20or%20someone%20may%20have%20leaked%20their%20movements%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERain%2C%20And%20A%20Fire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBursts%20of%20heavy%20rain%20since%20Saturday%20morning%20have%20made%20the%20operation%20more%20difficult%20both%20by%20reducing%20visibility%20and%20by%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20drones%20to%20operate.%20A%20fire%20also%20broke%20out%20near%20the%20cave%20where%20the%20terrorists%20are%20hiding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Changing%20Strategy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20terrorists%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20a%20two-day%20encounter%20in%20Rajouri%20district's%20Narla%20area%2C%20which%20began%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20three%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Uri%20sector%20of%20Baramulla%20when%20they%20were%20attempting%20to%20cross%20into%20India%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%20The%20Army%20said%20Pakistani%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffiring-by-pak-post-in-vicinity-army-after-3-terrorists-shot-dead-in-uri-sector-4395203%5C%22%3Egave%20covering%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20the%20terrorists%20cross%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20and%20the%20gunfire%20from%20the%20other%20side%20also%20%26quot%3Binterfered%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20efforts%20to%20retrieve%20the%20body%20of%20the%20third%20terrorist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Baramulla%20encounter%20makes%20it%20the%20forces'%20third%20brush%20with%20terrorists%20in%20just%20five%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20encounter%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20SP%20Vaid%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20operation%20in%20Anantnag%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20and%20there%20is%20a%2075-80%20degree%20steep%20climb.%20There%20is%20a%20dense%20forest%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20ditch%20on%20the%20other.%20It%20is%20very%20difficult%20for%20our%20forces%20when%20the%20terrorists%20hide%20in%20such%20a%20place.%20The%20terrorists%20are%20at%20a%20height%20and%20the%20personnel%20become%20vulnerable%20to%20attack%20when%20they%20try%20to%20ascend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20new%20strategy.%20A%20similar%20thing%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20Rajouri-Poonch%20recently%2C%20where%20the%20terrorists%20chose%20a%20hilly%20and%20forested%20area%20to%20hide%20in.%20For%20some%20time%20now%2C%20I%20have%20been%20noticing%20that%20the%20terrorists%20have%20been%20changing%20their%20strategy%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20establishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaid%20pointed%20out%20that%20when%20the%20Indian%20security%20forces%20began%20Operation%20All%20Out%20in%202017%2C%20thousands%20of%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20and%20they%20also%20began%20facing%20a%20shortage%20of%20AK-47s.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20a%20change%20in%20policy%20then%20and%20the%20terrorists%20started%20using%20pistols%20and%20small%20arms%20to%20target%20migrants%2C%20labourers%20and%20panchayat%20members%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20derail%20development.%20There%20had%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20such%20incidents%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20international%20attention%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20forces%20managed%20to%20control%20that%2C%20a%20new%20trend%20is%20visible%20now%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20in%20Rajouri-Poonch%20and%20now%20in%20nearby%20Anantnag.%20Unlike%20in%20the%20past%2C%20terrorists%20are%20avoiding%20inhabited%20areas%2C%20where%20they%20can%20be%20easily%20surrounded%2C%20and%20are%20now%20hiding%20in%20thick%20jungles%20and%20hilly%20areas.%20This%20helps%20them%20draw%20out%20the%20forces%20and%20harm%20them%2C%20and%20the%20terrain%20gives%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20escape%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20top%20cop%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20trying%20to%20drag%20out%20encounters%20for%20three%20to%20four%20days%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20the%20international%20media's%20attention%20as%20well.%20I%20think%20there%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20the%20strategy%20and%20we%20will%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694878680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fc1ghm93o_anantnag-encounter-650_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanantnag-encounter-jammu-and-kashmir-80-hours-and-counting-heres-why-the-j-k-encounter-is-dragging-on-4395867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Well-trained%20terrorists%2C%20the%20challenging%20terrain%2C%20dense%20forests%20and%20now%20inclement%20weather%20have%20all%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20encounter%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Anantnag%20stretching%20into%20the%20fourth%20day%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanantnag-encounter-jammu-and-kashmir-80-hours-and-counting-heres-why-the-j-k-encounter-is-dragging-on-4395867%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanantnag-encounter-jammu-and-kashmir-80-hours-and-counting-heres-why-the-j-k-encounter-is-dragging-on-4395867%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanantnag-encounter-jammu-and-kashmir-80-hours-and-counting-heres-why-the-j-k-encounter-is-dragging-on-4395867%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20rejects%20INDIA%20bloc%20decision%20to%20boycott%20show%20of%2014%20news%20anchors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694878584000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103719453%2Cimgsize-24530.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat