se%2C%20as%20well%20as%20replenish%20the%20budget%20of%20the%20aggressor%20country%2C%20thereby%20financing%20the%20war%E2%80%9D.%20The%20agency%20described%20the%20list%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpowerful%20reputational%20tool%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2Fjwat3snA%5C%22%3Ecooperation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.refinitiv.com%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fworld-check-kyc-screening%5C%22%3EWorld%20Check%20Database%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20to%20assess%20financial%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnazk.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fbloody-diamonds-the-nacp-lists-one-of-the-world-s-largest-diamond-producers-srk-on-the-list-of-international-war-sponsors%2F%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20NACP%20on%20September%2015%20announced%20that%20Shree%20Ramakrishna%20Exports%20was%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20sponsors%E2%80%9D%2C%20becoming%20the%20second%20company%20from%20India%20on%20the%20Ukrainian%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fukraine-accuses-three-indians-of-russian-propaganda%5C%22%3EUkraine%20Accuses%203%20Indians%2C%20Including%20Former%20NSAB%20Head%2C%20of%20%E2%80%98Promoting%20Russian%20Propaganda%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20company%20continues%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20aggressor%2C%20purchasing%20diamonds%20in%20Russia%2C%20despite%20the%20sanctions%20imposed%20against%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20in%20this%20sphere.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20company%20tripled%20the%20purchase%20of%20diamonds%20in%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20compared%20to%202021%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20citation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20note%20added%20that%20while%20other%20Western%20companies%20%E2%80%9Cbypass%20the%20Russian%20market%2C%20Shree%20Ramakrishna%20Exports%20actively%20buys%20Russian%20diamonds%20on%20favourable%20terms%2C%20thereby%20actively%20sponsoring%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20largest%20diamond%20reserves%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Russia%20is%20the%20biggest%20exporter%20of%20rough%20diamonds.%20More%20than%2090%25%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20diamond%20mining%20capacity%20is%20held%20by%20Russian%20firm%2C%20Alrosa%2C%20which%20is%20partly%20owned%20by%20the%20state.%20Following%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20the%20United%20States%20had%20issued%20sanctions%20against%20Alrosa.%20However%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20brought%20%241.5%20billion%20worth%20of%20Russian%20diamonds%20last%20year%20as%20it%20has%20not%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20Alrosa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20stands%20out%20as%20one%20of%20the%20few%20major%20economies%20that%20have%20refrained%20from%20publicly%20denouncing%20Russia%20for%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20opting%20to%20abstain%20on%20United%20Nations%20resolutions%20critical%20of%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Alrosa%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Feurope%2Frussias-alrosa-reports-strong-diamond-sales-despite-sanctions-2023-08-14%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20financial%20results%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20February%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20It%20said%20that%20diamond%20sales%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%20were%20at%20the%20same%20levels%20as%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Ukraine%20listed%20the%20Indian%20diamond%20firm%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20sponsor%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffr.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F1-g7-announce-russian-diamonds-090828123.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20G-7%20group%20of%20industrialised%20nations%20will%20soon%20announce%20an%20import%20ban%20on%20Russian%20diamonds%2C%20but%20admitted%20that%20the%20implementation%20would%20depend%20heavily%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20current%20rules%2C%20Russian%20diamonds%20cut%20and%20polished%20outside%2C%20are%20considered%20originating%20from%20the%20country%20that%20%E2%80%9Csubstantially%20transforms%E2%80%9D%20them.%20More%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20diamonds%20are%20cut%20and%20polished%20in%20India.%20There%20had%20been%20disquiet%20among%20G-7%20countries%20that%20this%20was%20a%20loophole%20that%20allowed%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20diamond%20industry%20to%20keep%20on%20expanding%20despite%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20G-7%20rules%20would%20permit%20India%20to%20process%20diamonds%20regardless%20of%20their%20origin%20while%20requiring%20that%20Russian%20diamonds%20be%20specifically%20identified%20and%20separated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsrk.one%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20its%20website%2C%20Shree%20Ramakrishna%20Exports%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20itself%20unjustly%20a%20target%20in%20the%20web%20of%20global%20geopolitics%2C%20misinformation%2C%20and%20baseless%20allegations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20accusations%20by%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20NACP%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20with%20an%20apparent%20intent%20to%20tarnish%20India%E2%80%99s%20diamond%20industry%20by%20pointing%20to%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20brands%20in%20the%20Indian%20trade%20%E2%80%93%20SRK%2C%20and%20thereby%20causing%20reputational%20damage%20to%20SRK%2C%20without%20any%20factual%20basis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20SRK%20does%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20endorse%20or%20support%E2%80%9D%20any%20conflict%2C%20the%20company%20asserted%20that%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20engaged%20in%20any%20transactions%20with%20UN%2C%20US%2C%20Indian%20or%20OFAC%20sanctioned%20entities%20or%20individuals%20involved%20in%20any%20form%20of%20conflict%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20Indian%20firm%20%E2%80%9Creserved%20right%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20relevant%20agency%20to%20protect%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20and%20In