he%20Airport%20Express%20Line%20at%20a%20massive%20speed%20of%20120%20kilometres%20per%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DMRC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20India%20International%20Convention%20and%20Expo%20Centre%20(IICC)%2C%20named%20YashoBhoomi%2C%20in%20Dwarka%20and%20also%20the%20extension%20of%20Delhi%20Metro's%20Airport%20Express%20Line%20from%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20to%20a%20new%20metro%20station%20at%20Dwarka%20Sector%2025%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extension%20of%20Delhi%20Metro's%20Airport%20Express%20Line%20from%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20to%20Yashobhoomi%20Dwarka%20Sector%2025%20will%20become%20operational%20from%203%20pm%20onwards%20on%20September%2017%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20on%20Saturday%20said%20the%20enhanced%20speed%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20implemented%20on%20this%20line%20after%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Airport%20Line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20operational%20Airport%20Express%20Line%20spans%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20metro%20station%20to%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20journey%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Yashobhoomi%20Dwarka%20Sector-25%20will%20take%20about%2021%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20was%20approximately%2022%20minutes%2C%20and%20now%20it%20has%20reduced%20to%20around%2019%20minutes%20between%20these%20two%20stations%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20saving%20of%20three%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approximate%20travel%20time%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Terminal%203%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20will%20be%20about%2015%20minutes%20and%2030%20seconds.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20more%20than%2018%20minutes%2C%20the%20DMRC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20trains%20at%20such%20a%20high%20speed%2C%20over%202.6%20lakh%20tension%20clamps%20were%20replaced%20on%20the%20entire%20corridor.%20The%20bulk%20of%20the%20work%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20night%20time%20from%2011%20pm%20till%207%20am%20to%20ensure%20minimal%20hindrance%20to%20the%20smooth%20operation%20of%20services.%20Over%20100%20workers%20were%20deployed%20at%20a%20time%20for%20this%20work%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20up%20this%20mammoth%20exercise%2C%20the%20efficacy%20of%20these%20clamps%20was%20checked%20on%20a%20kilometre-long%20trial%20track.%20Various%20measurements%20including%20vibration%20and%20stresses%20on%20rails%20were%20carried%20out%20using%20advanced%20instruments%20on%20this%20trial%20track%20before%20implementing%20the%20same%20on%20the%20main%20corridor%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estimated%20timeline%20for%20the%20completion%20of%20this%20task%20was%2018%20months.%20However%2C%20the%20DMRC%20took%20the%20challenge%20and%20successfully%20ensured%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20work%20within%20just%20six%20months%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20highly%20advanced%20system%20consisting%20of%203D%20accelerometers%20and%20strain%20censors%20was%20deployed%20for%20continuous%20measurement%20of%20vibrations%20and%20strains%20on%20the%20tracks%20at%20different%20speed%20levels.%20Oscillation%20monitoring%20was%20performed%20at%20speeds%20from%2090%20kmph%20to%20120%20kmph%20to%20ascertain%20smooth%20movement%20at%20higher%20speed%20levels%2C%20the%20DMRC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETremendous%20efforts%20were%20put%20in%20by%20DMRC%20officials%20to%20analyse%20the%20measurement%20data%20at%20various%20speeds%20to%20understand%20the%20behaviour%20and%20response%20of%20the%20system%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20signalling%20infrastructure%20also%20required%20verification%20of%20all%20software%20and%20safety%20certifications%20of%20the%20main%20system%20and%20the%20subsystems%20at%20such%20high%20speed.%20The%20interface%20t