was%20about%20the%20story%20we%20are%20telling%2C%20the%20impact%20this%20film%20is%20going%20to%20have%20on%20this%20amazing%20audience.%26quot%3B%20On%20working%20with%20SRK%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Shah%20Rukh%20and%20I%20are%20working%20together%2C%20we%20are%20not%20just%20co-stars%2C%20it's%20not%20formal%2C%20there%20is%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20and%20that's%20what%20always%20comes%20through%20in%20our%20work.%26quot%3B%20Atlee%20also%20talked%20about%20their%20chemistry%20in%20the%20film.%20Shah%20Rukh%20added%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20approaching%20Deepika%20for%20Aishwarya%20in%20Jawan%20came%20to%20him%20while%20she%20was%20filming%20%3Cem%3EPathaan's%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBesharam%20Rang%3C%2Fem%3E.%20SRK%20said%20he%20was%20sitting%20and%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20play%20a%20mother.%20%26quot%3BDeepika%20proved%20that%20she%20is%20a%20large-size%20actor%2C%20a%20big-size%20actor%20genuinely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nayanthara%20was%20unable%20to%20attend%20the%20Jawan%20press%20conference%2C%20she%20sent%20a%20video%20message%20in%20her%20place.%20She%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20be%20present%20in%20front%20of%20the%20media.%20She%20expressed%20her%20gratitude%20for%20the%20outpouring%20of%20love%20and%20support%2C%20saying%20it%20meant%20the%20world%20to%20her.%20She%20also%20congratulated%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20praised%20his%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20Rukh%20also%20said%20during%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20celebration.%20We%20rarely%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20live%20with%20a%20film%20for%20years.%20The%20making%20of%C2%A0Jawan%C2%A0has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20years%20due%20to%20Covid%20and%20time%20constraints.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20involved%20in%20this%20film%2C%20especially%20people%20from%20the%20South%20who%20came%20and%20settled%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20have%20been%20living%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20and%20working