C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9h9h6nno_akshay_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khans-shout-out-to-the-jawan-actors-from-the-south-4396050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIsme%20hum%20apni%20jaan%20laga%20denge%20%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Rohit%20Shetty%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khans-shout-out-to-the-jawan-actors-from-the-south-4396050%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khans-shout-out-to-the-jawan-actors-from-the-south-4396050%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khans-shout-out-to-the-jawan-actors-from-the-south-4396050%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Need%20To%20Fight%20Together%20With%20INDIA%20Bloc%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20Unity%20Message%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20President%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20used%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20reconstituted%20top%20decision-making%20body%20of%20the%20party%20to%20send%20out%20a%20strong%20signal%20of%20unity%20to%20the%2028-member%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20on%20Saturday.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20told%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20that%20the%20party%20has%20to%20fight%20unitedly%20with%20INDIA%20against%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20remarks%20come%20days%20after%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20its%20Coordination%20Committee%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar.%C2%A0They%20assume%20importance%20because%20of%20reports%20that%20the%20bloc%2C%20while%20largely%20successful%20in%20figuring%20out%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20in%20some%20states%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20tough%20time%20in%20others%2C%20especially%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20also%20said%20that%20they%20would%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20%26quot%3Btogether%20as%20far%20as%20possible%26quot%3B.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20the%20phrase%20in%20their%20resolution%20had%20raised%20eyebrows%20and%20lent%20credence%20to%20speculation%20that%20the%20parties%20were%20also%20seeing%20a%20rocky%20road%20ahead%20when%20it%20came%20to%20working%20out%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20in%20some%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20the%20CWC%20meeting%20-%20the%20first%20since%20he%20took%20over%20as%20the%20Congress%20president%20last%20year%20-%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Centre%20and%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20failure%20on%20all%20important%20fronts%E2%80%9D.%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20control%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%2C%20widening%20inequality%20or%20the%20deteriorating%20condition%20of%20farmers%20and%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20India%20is%20at%20a%20crossroads%20and%20is%20facing%20many%20internal%20challenges%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20witnessing%20the%20tragic%20events%20that%20are%20still%20unfolding%20in%20Manipur.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Modi%20government%20allowed%20the%20fire%20of%20Manipur%20to%20reach%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana.%20These%20incidents%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20a%20modern%2C%20progressive%2C%20and%20secular%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20danger%26quot%3B%20and%20rising%20prices%20have%20adversely%20affected%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20common%20man.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20the%20Centre's%20alleged%20negligence%20on%20China's%20encroachments%20poses%20a%20critical%20danger%20to%20the%20country's%20security%2C%20but%20the%20government%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20distract%20from%20real%20issues%20with%20%26quot%3Bempty%20slogans%26quot%3B%20like%20'Amritkaal'%20and%20'Third-Largest%20Economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20three%20successful%20meetings%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20forging%20ahead%20to%20combat%20the%20anti-people%20and%20anti-democratic%20BJP%20government.%20Perturbed%20by%20this%20development%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20resorting%20to%20vindictive%20action%20against%20Opposition%20parties.%20We%20also%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20government's%20attempts%20to%20stifle%20opposition%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20curtail%20public%20scrutiny%20in%20parliament.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CWC%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20which%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20message%20to%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20in%20Telangana%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20be%20making%20all%20efforts%20to%20win%20the%20state%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20deliberated%20on%20the%20preparations%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20next%20year.%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20are%20among%20the%20panel's%20new%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20members%20of%20the%20top%20decision-making%20body%20include%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Union%20Ministers%20P%20Chidambaram%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694872620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fo3mctkbo_cwc-sonia-gandhi-650_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2