pp%20message%2C%20I%20was%20naturally%20devastated%2C%26quot%3B%20Hurst%20wrote%20in%20the%20book%20published%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20later%20that%20he%20had%20only%20married%20me%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20level%20of%20seniority%20in%20the%20company%20he%20worked%20at%20and%20he%20had%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20married%2C%20in%20order%20to%20be%20given%20the%20promotion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20and%20life%20coach%2C%20who%20married%20Looney%20in%202017%2C%20said%20that%20the%20way%20he%20ended%20their%20marriage%20was%20%26quot%3Bunbelievable%26quot%3B.%20She%20also%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bunexpected%20gift%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20divorced%20in%202019%2C%20three%20months%20before%20he%20became%20CEO%20of%20BP%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2Fbp-turtle-bernard-looney-deepwater-profits-b1106769.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EEvening%20Standard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELooney%20resigned%20as%20CEO%20of%20BP%20after%20less%20than%20four%20years%20in%20the%20role.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bp.com%2Fen%2Fglobal%2Fcorporate%2Fnews-and-insights%2Fpress-releases%2Fbp-ceo-resigns.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estatement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BP%20announced%20his%20departure%20following%20an%20investigation%20into%20his%20conduct%20and%20personal%20relationships%20with%20colleagues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20board%20was%20tipped%20off%20in%20May%202022%20about%20claims%20he'd%20had%20personal%20relationships%20with%20coworkers.%20In%20a%20review%20Looney%20%26quot%3Bdisclosed%20a%20small%20number%20of%20historical%20relationships%20with%20colleagues%20prior%20to%20becoming%20CEO.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20company%20said%20Looney%20breached%20its%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20but%20that%20it%20re