0student%20visas%20will%20be%20GBP%20127%20more%20expensive%20for%20travellers%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20legislation%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20UK%20Home%20Office%20said%20the%20changes%20mean%20that%20the%20cost%20for%20a%20visit%20visa%20for%20less%20than%20six%20months%20will%20rise%20to%20GBP%20115%20and%20the%20fee%20for%20applying%20for%20a%20student%20visa%20from%20outside%20the%20UK%20will%20rise%20to%20GBP%20490%20%E2%80%93%20to%20equal%20the%20amount%20charged%20for%20in-country%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20after%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20had%20announced%20in%20July%20that%20the%20fees%20and%20health%20surcharge%20paid%20towards%20the%20UK's%20state-funded%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20by%20visa%20applicants%20are%20set%20to%20rise%20%E2%80%9Csignificantly%E2%80%9D%20to%20meet%20the%20country's%20public%20sector%20wage%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20going%20to%20increase%20the%20charges%20that%20we%20have%20for%20migrants%20who%20are%20coming%20to%20this%20country%20when%20they%20apply%20for%20visas%20and%20indeed%20something%20called%20the%20Immigration%20Health%20Surcharge%20(IHS)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20levy%20that%20they%20pay%20to%20access%20the%20NHS%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20those%20fees%20are%20going%20to%20go%20up%20and%20that%20will%20raise%20over%20GBP%201%20billion%2C%20so%20across%20the%20board%20visa%20application%20fees%20are%20going%20to%20go%20up%20significantly%20and%20similarly%20for%20the%20IHS%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Office%20indicated%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20most%20work%20and%20visit%20visas%2C%20and%20an%20increase%20of%20at%20least%2020%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20priority%20visas%2C%20study%20visas%20and%20certificates%20of%20sponsorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIncome%20from%20fees%20charged%20plays%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20Home%20Office's%20ability%20to%20run%20a%20sustainable%20immigration%20and%20nationality%20system.%20Careful%20consideration%20is%20given%20when%20setting%20fees%20to%20help%20reduce%20the%20funding%20contribution%20from%20British%20taxpayers%2C%20whilst%20continuing%20to%20provide%20a%20service%20that%20remains%20attractive%20to%20those%20wishing%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20support%20broader%20prosperity%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Home%20Office%20said%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hike%20in%20fees%20applies%20across%20most%20visa%20categories%2C%20including%20health%20and%20care%20visa%3B%20applications%20to%20register%20and%20naturalise%20as%20a%20British%20citizen%3B%20fees%20for%20up%20to%20six%20months%2C%20two%2C%20five%20and%2010-year%20visit%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hike%20also%20applies%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20fees%20for%20entry%20clearance%20and%20certain%20applications%20for%20leave%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20including%20those%20for%20work%20and%20study%3B%20fees%20for%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20enter%20and%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20remain%3B%20and%20fees%20in%20relation%20to%20certificates%20of%20sponsorship%20and%20confirmation%20of%20acceptance%20for%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20are%20subject%20to%20parliamentary%20approval%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20force%20from%20October%204%2C%20the%20Home%20Office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694869920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fuk-visa-generic_650x400_51453218458.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-visa-fee-hike-for-visitors-students-to-be-effective-from-october-4-4395552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20B