ior%20military%20commanders%20in%20charge%20of%20its%20nukes%2C%20China%20is%20now%20investigating%20its%20defense%20minister%2C%20US%20officials%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22General%20Li%20Shangfu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650580f2f05aa00019bd9495%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeneral%20Li%20Shangfu.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Nemenov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGeneral%20Li%20Shangfu%2C%20China's%20defense%20minister%2C%20hasn't%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20officials%20have%20said%20Li%20is%20under%20investigation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F15%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fxi-china-military-general-li-shangfu.html%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELi%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20corruption%20over%20the%20procurement%20of%20military%20equipment%2C%20reports%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20said%20China's%20defense%20minister%20Li%20Shangfu%20was%20under%20investigation%20by%20authorities%20and%20had%20likely%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20position%20after%20he%20was%20taken%20away%20for%20questioning%20by%20authorities%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-defense-minister-has-been-removed-from-post-u-s-officials-say-ae0761f4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20Chinese%20military%20said%20the%20defense%20minister%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fus-diplomat-questions-whether-chinese-defence-minister-under-house-arrest-2023-09-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%