20Defense%20and%20Security%20Research%2C%20a%20Taiwan-funded%20think-tank%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F15%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fxi-china-military-general-li-shangfu.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20investigation%20signaled%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20face%26quot%3B%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20who%20had%20appointed%20General%20Li%20to%20the%20post%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20force%20him%20from%20power%2C%20but%20it%20will%20erode%20his%20prestige%20as%20ruler%2C%26quot%3B%20Su%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Li%2C%2065%2C%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20for%20almost%20three%20weeks%2C%20and%20he%20canceled%20a%20scheduled%20meeting%20he%20was%20due%20to%20attend%20in%20Vietnam%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fchinas-defence-minister-not-seen-weeks-skipped-vietnam-meet-2023-09-14%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERahm%20Emanuel%2C%20the%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Japan%2C%20wondered%20if%20Li%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bplaced%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAmbJapan%2Fstatus%2F1702493699966484830%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-defense-minister-under-investigation-military-commanders-replaced-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694863191000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650580f2f05aa00019bd9495%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-defense-minister-under-investigation-military-commanders-replaced-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A