-and-history-of-davids-bridal-and-wedding-dresses-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eability%20to%20appeal%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20brides%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20keeps%20CEO%20Jim%20Marcum%20optimistic%20about%20the%20company's%20future%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20sat%20down%20with%20Insider%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20bankruptcy%2C%20subsequent%20sale%2C%20and%20the%20seismic%20shifts%20happening%20in%20the%20wedding%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222963%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David's%20Bridal%20CEO%20Jim%20Marcum%20sits%20on%20a%20green%20couch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650497e2956dba001aceae33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJim%20Marcum%20became%20the%20CEO%20of%20David's%20Bridal%20in%202019.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20and%20condensed%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20with%20David's%20Bridal%20recently.%20How%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20the%20company%20and%20its%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20excitement%20in%20the%20company%20right%20now%2C%20actually.%20The%20teams%20are%20motivated.%20David's%20is%20back.%20We've%20gotten%20our%20customer-service%20scores%20of%20thousands%20of%20reviews%20a%20month%20up%20to%204.9%20stars%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20bankruptcy%2C%20we%20kept%20our%20field%20teams%20intact%2C%20stayed%20focused%20on%20the%20customer.%20We%20promised%20the%20consumer%20that%20we'd%20deliver%20on%20every%20order%2C%20every%20dress.%20They%20stuck%20true%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20our%20bankruptcy%2C%20we%20averaged%204.8%20stars%2C%20which%20is%20kind%20of%20amazing.%20Now%20that%20we%20have%20this%20successful%20transaction%2C%20the%20morale%20is%20very%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThrough%20the%20sale%2C%20how%20did%20the%20company%20attempt%20to%20save%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20our%20goal%20all%20along%20to%20find%20that%20right%20partner%20that%20understood%20retail%20and%20could%20understand%20the%20impacts%20that%20were%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20close%20approximately%20100%20stores%2C%20and%20we%20spent%20an%20extensive%20amount%20of%20time%20evaluating%20our%20real%20estate%20footprint%20and%20the%20ideal%20number%20of%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stores%20that%20we%20closed%20represented%20about%2010%25%20of%20our%20four-wall%20contributions.%20Whereas%20the%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20stores%20we're%20going%20forward%20with%2C%20represent%20approximately%2090%25.%20So%20it's%20getting%20down%20to%20a%20more%20nimble%2C%20profitable%20store%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20half%20the%20store%20closures%20were%20in%20markets%20where%20we%20already%20had%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20A%20company%20representative%20later%20clarified%20that%20the%20stores%20closing%20represented%207%25%20of%20four-wall%20contributions%2C%20which%20is%20a%20profitability%20metric.%20The%20stores%20staying%20open%20represent%20approximately%2093%25.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20seen%20changes%20in%20demand%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmicro-weddings-are-way-better-cheaper-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ehow%20weddings%20are%20changing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Covid%20hit%2C%20there%20were%20some%20trends%20where%20you%20saw%20the%20minimony.%20They'd%20go%20get%20married%20in%20the%20backyard%20because%20travel%20was%20restricted.%20If%20they%20did%20have%20a%20bridal%20party%2C%20it%20was%20the%20maid%20of%20honor%20and%20not%20an%20entire%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20seen%20the%20bride%20tell%20us%20about%20her%20budget.%20Inflation%20put%20an%20economic%20concern%20on%20the%20price%20of%20her%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uniqueness%20about%20David's%20is%20we%20have%20dresses%20in%20the%20%24199%20price%20point%2C%20and%20we've%20got%20dresses%20at%20%242%2C000.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20aesthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20see%20bridal%20parties%20constrict.%20On%20average%2C%20we%20would%20run%203.08%20bridesmaids%20prior%20to%20Covid.%20We%20saw%20that%20dip%20as%20low%20as%202.6.%20That's%20coming%20back%20as%20the%20market%20opens%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David's%20Bridal%20wedding%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58ea5c54dd0895bc698b4af2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221714%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20dresses%20range%20from%20%24199%20to%20%242%2C000%2C%20Marcum%20said.%3Cp%3ERandy%20Brooke%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20pandemic%20taught%20many%20retailers%20that%20the%20just-in-time%20model%20was%20not%20beneficial%20for%20today's%20consumer.%20What%20did%20David's%20learn%20about%20its%20supply%20chain%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20validated%20was%20the%20power%20of%20that%20vertical%20supply%20chain.%20We%20had%20factories%20that%20would%20shut%20down%20in%20one%20country%2C%20or%20restrictions%20in%20one%20country%20so%20we%20had%20to%20shift%20the%20production%20of%20raw%20materials%20from%20that%20country%20to%20another%20country.%20Then%20no%20sooner%20than%20we%20do%20that%2C%20we'd%20have%20to%20shift%20it%20to%20another%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelivery%20to%20the%20customer%2C%20we%20never%20missed.%20When%20that%20boat%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20Suez%20Canal%2C%20we%20had%20dresses%20on%20it.%20When%20that%20boat%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20Baltimore%20Harbor%2C%20we%20had%20containers%20of%20dresses%20on%20those%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20dresses%20where%20we%20would%20put%20that%20unit%20back%20into%20production%20in%20a%20factory%20and%2048%20hours%20later%20had%20it%20on%20the%20belly%20of%20an%20airplane%20flying%20it%20into%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20one%20dress%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20why%2C%20when%20we%20filed%20this%20bankruptcy%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20thought%20I%20was%20absolutely%20crazy%20for%20making%20the%20claim%20that%20we%20would%20deliver%20on%20every%20dress%2C%20on%20every%20order%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20customer%20had%20the%20confidence%20that%20she%20could%20continue%20to%20shop%20at%20David%20Bridal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20has%20a%20reputation%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BWalmart%20of%20Bridal.%26quot%3B%20How%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20that%20name%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20we%20could%20be%20better%20positioned%20than%20any%20retailer%20in%20this%20country%20for%20the%20segment%20we're%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20what%20way%20are%20you%20better%20positioned%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20targeting%20mass%20America.%20I've%20heard%20that%20comment%20about%20Walmart%20so%20many%20times.%20I%20challenge%20Walmart%20to%20be%204.9%20stars%20in%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20sell%20more%20wedding%20dresses%20on%20a%20weekend%20than%20a%20boutique%20will%20sell%2C%20oftentimes%20not%20only%20in%20a%20month%2C%20but%20an%20entire%20season.%20About%2025%25%20of%20marriages%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20second%20marriages.%20Average%20age%20is%20over%2040.%20And%20we%20did%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20that.%20First-time%20brides%2C%20their%20average%20age%20is%20a%20little%20under%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20really%20look%20at%20our%20dresses%2C%20you%20can't%20get%20the%20value%2C%20price%20proposition%2C%20or%20quality%20anywhere%20at%20our%20price%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20walks%20by%20exterior%20of%20David's%20Bridal%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643d8ba2cd8ca0001919076f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20is%20targeting%20mass%20America%2C%20Marcum%20said.%20%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you're%20not%20afraid%20of%20competitors%20taking%20market%20share%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20competitors%20have%20tried%2C%20and%20there%20are%20competitors%20out%20there%20that%20I%20respect.%20It%20is%20about%20helping%20that%20bride%20for%20her%20entire%20village.%20We%20have%20occasion%2C%20we%20have%20mother%20of%20the%20bride%2C%20we%20have%20the%20flower%20girl%2C%20we%20have%20the%20bridesmaids%2C%20we%20have%20gifts%2C%20we%20have%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20we%20launched%20Pearl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20it's%20very%20similar%20to%20The%20Knot%20where%20you%20can%20plan%20your%20wedding.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20so%20now%20we%20have%20wedding-planning%20checklists%20and%20vision%20boards%20that%20allow%20you%20to%20curate%20the%20style%20of%20your%20wedding.%20We%20have%20the%20registry%2C%20and%20now%20we%20have%20the%20vendor%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20we%20did%20that%20was%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20the%20bride%20way%20upfront%20when%20she%20first%20got%20engaged.%20Eighty-five%20to%2090%25%20of%20all%20brides%20will%20come%20into%20our%20funnel.%20They%20don't%20all%20buy%20their%20dresses%20with%20us.%20That's%20okay.%20But%20there's%20a%20chance%20if%20they%20don't%20buy%20their%20wedding%20dress%20with%20us%2C%20their%20bridesmaids%20or%20their%20mother%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20convinced%20you%20that%20maybe%20brides%20would%20turn%20to%20Pearl%20instead%20of%20somewhere%20like%20The%20Knot%20that%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20many%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20so%20many%20facets%20to%20that.%20The%20first%20thing%20brides%20Google%20when%20they%20get%20engaged%20is%20planning.%20David's%20is%20a%20highly%20recognizable%20name.%20Over%20half%20our%20traffic%20is%20generic%20traffic%20because%20it's%20top-of-mind%20brand%20awareness.%20The%20brides%20are%20coming%20in%20and%20they%20need%20information%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Knot's%20value%20prop%20is%20the%20vendors.%20These%20entrepreneurs%20take%20crazy%20money%20to%20get%20those%20leads.%20So%20when%20we%20designed%20Pearl%2C%20we%20took%20a%20really%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20economics%20of%20what%20we%20would%20charge%20a%20vendor%20to%20list.%20The%20majority%20of%20it%20is%20free.%20To%20us%2C%20it%20was%20about%20the%20ecosystem%20to%20offer%20the%20bride%20something%20that's%20of%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David's%20Bridal%20bridesmaid%20dresses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65047ecf956dba001ace7eb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid's%20Bridal%20sells%20bridal%20gowns%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bridesmaid%2C%20prom%2C%20and%20special%20occasion%20dresses.%20%3Cp%3EDavid's%20Bridal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-knot-vendors-worth-price-busy-wedding-year-weddingwire-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eeveryone%20dubbed%202022%20as%20the%20year%20of%20weddings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20That%20worked%20out%20for%20some%20people%20and%20didn't%20for%20others.%20Was%20it%20a%20boom%20year%20for%20David's%20Bridal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20boom%20year%20for%20anybody%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20would%20you%20say%20that%20was%20mostly%20a%20facade%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeddingWire%20published%20that%20story%20about%202022%20being%20the%20year%20of%20record%20weddings%20in%20early-%20to%20mid-2021.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20all%20these%20venues%20shut%20down%2C%20there%20were%20about%20a%20half-a-million%20weddings%20disrupted.%20There%20was%20a%20scramble%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20booked%20into%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20only%20so%20much%20capacity%2C%20so%20the%20venues%20got%20really%20restricted.%20They%20couldn't%20hire%20labor.%20All%20those%202020%20venues%20rolled%20into%202021.%20Then%20you%20had%20the%20Delta%20variants%2C%20some%20of%20those%20weddings%20rolled%20into%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20that%20why%20David's%20Bridal%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20this%20year%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20phenomenal%202021.%20We%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20that%20had%20the%20inventory%20when%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%20in%20the%20backyard.%20But%20what%20happened%20is%20that%20we%20got%20to%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202022%20and%20right%20after%20that%2C%202022%20was%20soft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20projecting%20much%20higher.%20We%20had%20the%20data%20once%20a%20bride%20booked%20an%20appointment.%20We%20converted%20her%20between%2065%20and%2070%25.%20That%20means%20she%20had%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20and%20we%20had%20the%20assortment.%20The%20question%20was%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20funnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20seeing%20any%20seismic%20shift%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESignet%20Jewelers%20has%20projected%20that%20engagement%20sales%20will%20need%20to%20grow%2025%25%20by%202026%20to%20return%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%20What%20does%20that%20mean%20for%20the%20future%20of%20David's%20Bridal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20they%20believe%20that%20softening%20occurred%20is%20because%20of%20Covid%20when%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20you%20either%20had%20a%20relationship%20or%20you%20didn't.%20You%20heard%20about%20all%20these%20engagements%2C%20which%20led%20to%202021%20being%20good%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%20three%20years%20in%20the%20dating%20cycle%20to%20get%20to%20the%20engagement.%20They%20put%20out%20projections%20for%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%20%E2%80%94%20they%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20robust%20and%20picking%20back%20up.%20And%20they've%20put%20out%20data%20projections%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20projections%20are%20halfway%20true%2C%20we%20feel%20very%20good.%20We're%20not%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-jim-marcum-optimistic-about-future-after-bankruptcy-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6500bc7b1afe8f0019e90086%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-jim-marcum-optimistic-about-future-after-bankruptcy-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22David's%20Bridal%20CEO%20Jim%20Marcum%20discusses%20the%20wedding%20retailer's%20second%20bankruptcy%2C%20subsequent%20sale%2C%20and%20its%20future.%20%26quot%3BDavid's%20is%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcum%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jortakales%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-jim-marcum-optimistic-about-future-after-bankruptcy-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak's%20last%20ditch%20plan%20to%20save%20his%20job%3A%20Don't%20look%20back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103715423%2Cimgsize