%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btiny%20home%26quot%3B%20loft%20addition%20was%20about%20%2415%2C000%2C%20Jeff%20said%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20total%20spend%20of%20approximately%20%2450%2C000%20for%20the%20complete%20renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20come%20cheap%2C%20but%20the%20family%20told%20Insider%20that%20it's%20worth%20every%20penny%20because%20it's%20helped%20them%20live%20out%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20family%20motto%20is%20'do%20the%20dream%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20said.%20%26quot%3BDoing%20the%20dream%20is%20not%20necessarily%20simple.%20There's%20going%20to%20be%20hurdles%20and%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20things%20in%20your%20way%2C%20but%20the%20biggest%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20is%20just%20push%20through%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20payoff%20is%20so%20far%20beyond%20what%20you%20can%20imagine.%20It's%20so%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-family-tiny-home-roof-school-bus-diy-space-kids-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4f8b54dd2b50019c2cfae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-family-tiny-home-roof-school-bus-diy-space-kids-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DIY%20renovation%2C%20which%20cost%20%2415%2C000%2C%20involved%20the%20Batterton%20family%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Btiny%20home%26quot%3B%20on%20top%20of%20the%20roof%20of%20their%20converted%20school%20bus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-family-tiny-home-roof-school-bus-diy-space-kids-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22