ent%20of%20the%20trade%20mission%20by%20Canada%20comes%20after%20it%20had%20in%20August%20placed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpause%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Early%20Progress%20Trade%20Agreement%20(EPTA).%20The%20five-day%20Team%20Canada%20trade%20mission%20was%20to%20be%20led%20by%20Mary%20Ng%2C%20who%20is%20the%20minister%20of%20international%20trade%2C%20export%20promotion%2C%20small%20business%20and%20economic%20development.%20The%20visit%20of%20the%20Canadian%20trade%20mission%20to%20India%20was%20announced%20when%20Union%20commerce%20and%20industry%20minister%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20was%20in%20Canada%20for%20a%20bilateral%20visit%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20countries%20first%20launched%20negotiations%20for%20a%20trade%20deal%2013%20years%20ago%20in%202010%2C%20but%20there%20had%20been%20limited%20progress%20until%202022%20when%20negotiations%20began%20on%20a%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28151247%2FTrudeau1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-strained-ties-canada-indefinitely-postpones-planned-trade-mission-to-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Canada%20has%20not%20cited%20any%20reason%20officially%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20souring%20of%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20after%20India's%20critical%20remarks%20against%20Canada%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20arrest%20the%20secessionist%20Khalistani%20movement%20in%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-strained-ties-canada-indefinitely-postpones-planned-trade-mission-to-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay-Rohit%20Shetty%20to%20team%20up%20again%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103715221%2Cimgsize-37750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-and-rohit-shetty-to-collaborate-again-for-an-action-thriller-report%2Farticleshow%2F103715216.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103715216.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAkshay%20Kumar%20is%20reportedly%20set%20to%20collaborate%20with%20director%20Rohit%20Shetty%20and%20Mohit%20Suri%20for%20an%20action%20thriller.%20The%20script%20has%20aligned%20with%20their%20vision%20and%20will%20feature%20Kumar%20in%20a%20unique%20character.%20The%20movie%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20shooting%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Kumar's%20film%20'Mission%20Raniganj'%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20October%206%2C%20and%20he%20has%20several%20other%20projects%20in%20the%20pipeline%20including%20'Soorarai%20Pottru%2C'%20'Bade%20Miyan%20Chote%20Miyan%2C'%20and%20'Khel%20Khel%20Mein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-and-rohit-shetty-to-collaborate-again-for-an-action-thriller-report%2Farticleshow%2F103715216.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rudy%20Giuliani%20'may%20have%20been%20compromised'%20by%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20and%20FBI%20leaders%20didn't%20care%2C%20alleges%20special%20agent%20Johnathan%20Buma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rudy%20Giuliani%20and%20Johnathan%20Buma%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65049cd2956dba001aceb466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20video%20interview%2C%20FBI%20special%20agent%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20right%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20bureau%20stymied%20leads%20that%20implicated%20Donald%20Trump's%20personal%20attorney%20Rudy%20Giuliani.%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FGetty%2C%20Amelia%20Kosciulek%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20real%20story%20of%20the%20FBI%20and%20Trumpworld%20is%20very%20different%20than%20what%20many%20Americans%20have%20heard%2C%20an%20FBI%20special%20agent%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20exclusive%20video%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohnathan%20Buma%20says%20his%20FBI%20supervisors%20didn't%20care%20about%20his%20leads%20tying%20Giuliani%20to%20Russian%20intelligence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuma's%20disclosures%20to%20the%20Senate%20raise%20questions%20about%20Giuliani%20and%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20Hunter%20Biden-Burisma%20story.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20is%20gradually%20emerging%20as%20the%20ultimate%20referee%20in%20US%20politics.%20FBI%20agents%20were%20the%20ones%20to%20carry%20out%20Robert%20Mueller's%20Trump-Russia%20investigation.%20FBI%20agents%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20showed%20up%20with%20a%20search%20warrant%20at%20the%20gates%20of%20Mar-a-Lago.%20Today%2C%20FBI%20agents%20are%20doing%20the%20pick-and-shovel%20work%20of%20digging%20into%20Donald%20Trump's%20allegedly%20criminal%20actions%20on%20January%206.%20They%20are%20also%20investigating%20Hunter%20Biden%20for%20the%20firearm-related%20charges%20that%20he%20was%20indicted%20for%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20FBI%20holding%20so%20many%20cards%2C%20allegations%20of%20political%20bias%20within%20the%20bureau%20should%20concern%20everyone.%20Insider%20has%20now%20published%20a%20video%20interview%20with%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20a%2014-year%20special%20agent%20working%20out%20of%20the%20bureau's%20Los%20Angeles%20Field%20Office.%20Buma%20is%20a%20counter-intelligence%20specialist%20who%20speaks%20Russian%20and%20holds%20an%20active%20Top%20Secret%20security%20clearance.%20He%20first%20raised%20the%20alarm%20through%20legally%20sanctioned%20whistleblower%20channels%20inside%20the%20FBI%2C%20and%20he%20remains%20employed%20there%20to%20this%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Buma%2C%20the%20real%20story%20of%20the%20FBI%20during%20the%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20years%20is%20very%20different%20from%20the%20one%20that's%20being%20told%20in%20hearings%20held%20by%20the%20GOP-controlled%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20watch%20Insider's%20interview%20with%20Buma%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FHjw7OWyC-puACk8ZV.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22FBI%20whistleblower%20exposes%20alleged%20pro-Trump%20bias%20at%20the%20bureau%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20congressional%20staff%20member%20told%20Insider%20that%20Buma's%20allegations%20are%20being%20taken%20seriously%20on%20the%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Buma's%20statements%20raise%20serious%20concerns%20that%20Republicans'%20impeachment%20campaign%20is%20continuing%20to%20amplify%20a%20disinformation%20effort%20that%20has%20its%20sources%20in%20the%20Russian%20intelligence%20apparatus%20and%20could%20have%20been%20exposed%20and%20silenced%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20Giuliani%20and%20the%20FBI%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20ways%20in%20which%20Buma's%20account%20could%20transform%20the%20emerging%20picture%20of%20the%20FBI%20and%20its%20interactions%20with%20Trump's%20circle%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20FBI%20didn't%20care%20about%20Giuliani's%20possible%20Kremlin%20ties%2C%20Buma%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRudy%20Giuliani%20may%20have%20been%20compromised%20by%20individuals%20suspected%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20Russian%20counterintelligence%20influence%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Buma%20told%20Insider.%20And%20within%20the%20FBI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20important%20intelligence%20information%20being%20suppressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuma's%20concerns%20about%20Giuliani%2C%20a%20personal%20attorney%20for%20Trump%20during%20his%20presidency%2C%20center%20on%20the%20%24300%2C000%20his%20firm%20received%20from%20Pavel%20Fuks%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20oligarch%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Moscow.%20(A%20spokesperson%20for%20Fuks%20has%20denied%20that%20he%20has%20ties%20to%20the%20Russian%20security%20services.)%20Fuks%20traveled%20to%20Washington%20for%20Trump's%202017%20inaugural%2C%20and%20he%20had%20previously%20approached%20Trump%20about%20building%20a%20Trump%20Tower%20in%20Moscow.%20According%20to%20Buma's%20disclosure%2C%20an%20FBI%20Intelligence%20Information%20Report%20asserted%20that%20Fuks%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20co-opted%20asset%20of%20the%20RIS%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20Russian%20intelligence%20services.%20Fuks's%20%24300%2C000%20payment%20to%20Giuliani's%20firm%20coincided%20with%20trips%20Giuliani%20made%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20order%20to%20gather%20information%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20company%20Burisma%20and%20pressure%20Ukrainian%20officials%20to%20open%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuma%20says%20that%20he%20raised%20concerns%20about%20Giuliani's%20possible%20ties%20to%20Russian%20intelligence%20to%20his%20FBI%20superiors%2C%20and%20that%20they%20simply%20weren't%20interested%20in%20following%20up.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20he%20claims%2C%20they%20eventually%20prohibited%20Buma%20from%20doing%20any%20reporting%20related%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Efforts%20to%20focus%20US%20voters%20on%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%20in%202019%20were%20a%20bigger%20and%20longer-term%20operation%20than%20previously%20known%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20has%20always%20maintained%20that%20allegations%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20company%20that%20paid%20Biden%20as%20much%20as%20%2483%2C333%20a%20month%20to%20sit%20on%20its%20board%2C%20originated%20with%20Hunter's%20abandoned%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuma's%20disclosures%20suggest%20otherwise.%20Hunter%20Biden%20left%20his%20laptop%20at%20a%20computer%20repair%20store%20in%20April%202019.%20But%20months%20earlier%2C%20in%20January%202019%2C%20Buma%20says%20he%20brought%20three%20of%20his%20sources%20in%20to%20talk%20to%20Department%20of%20Justice%20prosecutors%20about%20Hunter%20Biden.%20They%20were%20pushing%20the%20same%20narrative%20that%20would%2C%20months%20later%2C%20turn%20into%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20talking%20point%3A%20Hunter's%20work%20for%20Burisma%20didn't%20just%20create%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20conflict%3B%20it%20was%20somehow%20illegal.%20The%20sources%20also%20claimed%20that%20George%20Soros%2C%20the%20billionaire%20who%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20numerous%20far-right%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Binvolved%20in%20massive%20money%20laundering%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Buma's%20disclosure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20exactly%20how%20the%20Hunter-Burisma%20story%20got%20started.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20Ukrainian%20sources%20were%20pushing%20Burisma%20allegations%20months%20before%20the%20laptop%20left%20Hunter%20Biden's%20hands%20adds%20to%20the%20body%20of%20evidence%20suggesting%20that%20Trump's%20favorite%20political%20storyline%20originated%20in%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0not%20Delaware%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20Giuliani%20was%20just%20one%20arm%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20inject%20those%20allegations%20into%20the%20US%20political%20system%20in%20advance%20of%20the%202020%20election.%20This%20happens%20to%20line%20up%20perfectly%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Ff%2F%3Fid%3D00000175-4393-d7aa-af77-579f9b330000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20much-maligned%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20by%20more%20than%2050%20intelligence%20community%20officials%20in%20advance%20of%20the%202020%20election%2C%20warning%20of%20foreign%20interference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Buma%20recalled%20telling%20an%20FBI%20colleague%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20this%20is%20the%20leading%20edge%20of%20a%20disinformation%20campaign%20to%20create%20a%20theme%20of%20derogatory%20information%20about%20the%20Bidens%20in%20anticipation%20that%20Biden%20will%20be%20Trump's%20main%20political%20rival%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuma's%20disclosure%20also%20points%20to%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20all%20the%20information%20attributed%20to%20Hunter%20Biden's%20abandoned%20laptop%20actually%20came%20from%20the%20laptop.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20went%20public%20with%20the%20laptop%20story%2C%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20the%202020%20election%2C%20Giuliani%20had%20been%20engaged%20in%20months-long%20effort%20%26quot%3Bto%20secure%20from%20Ukrainian%20and%20likely%20also%20Russian%20sources%20information%20that%20Giuliani%20believed%20would%20affect%20the%202020%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Buma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Bill%20Barr's%20DOJ%20fired%20Geoffrey%20Berman%20at%20a%20very%20convenient%20time%20%E2%80%94%20for%20Rudy%20Giuliani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20Buma's%20stymied%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20Giuliani%20was%20an%20undercover%20operation%20that%20was%20suddenly%20shut%20down%2C%20Buma%20said%2C%20shortly%20before%20Geoffrey%20Berman%2C%20the%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20whose%20office%20would%20have%20authorized%20the%20operation%2C%20was%20fired%20by%20then-Attorney%20General%20Bill%20Barr.%20Barr%20and%20Berman%20have%20both%20declined%20to%20comment%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FBI%20special%20agent%20Johnathan%20Buma%20has%20sought%20whistleblower%20protections%20and%20says%20he's%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20workplace%20discrimination%20by%20his%20supervisors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6504b016916aab00192f4e47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFBI%20special%20agent%20Johnathan%20Buma%20has%20sought%20whistleblower%20protections%20and%20says%20he's%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20workplace%20retaliation%20by%20his%20supervisors.%3Cp%3EAmelia%20Kosciulek%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Alleged%20political%20bias%20within%20the%20FBI%20cuts%20both%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20FBI%20agents%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20bureau%20is%20out%20to%20get%20Trump.%20Some%20have%20received%20financial%20support%20from%20conservative%20donors%3B%20all%20have%20been%20given%20a%20platform%20by%20the%20GOP-controlled%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20Buma%2C%20we're%20not%20getting%20the%20full%20story.%20Working%20out%20of%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Field%20Office%2C%20Buma%20gives%20a%20firsthand%20account%20of%20a%20dynamic%20that%20is%20exactly%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20has%20been%20alleged%3A%20Information%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20was%20eagerly%20received%20and%20handed%20off%20to%20the%20case%20agents%20while%20investigations%20into%20Giuliani%20were%20shut%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20employees%20scattered%20across%20dozens%20of%20field%20offices%2C%20is%20both%20ideologically%20diverse%20and%20unusually%20decentralized%20for%20a%20federal%20agency.%20A%20common%20FBI%20maxim%20is%20that%20there%20are%20four%20bureaus%20within%20the%20bureau%20%E2%80%94%20headquarters%2C%20the%20Washington%20Field%20Office%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Field%20Office%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20FBI.%20Buma's%20disclosures%20are%20a%20reminder%20to%20be%20skeptical%20of%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20score%20political%20points%20by%20painting%20the%20bureau%20with%20too%20broad%20a%20brush.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20of%20the%20GOP's%20congressional%20hearings%20%26quot%3Baren't%20getting%20the%20full%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Buma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20It%20isn't%20easy%20being%20a%20whistleblower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20going%20through%20approved%20FBI%20channels%20to%20register%20his%20concerns%2C%20Buma%20alleges%20that%20the%20bureau%20retaliated%20against%20him%2C%20which%20is%20prohibited%20by%20the%20Whistleblower%20Protection%20Act.%20He%20says%20he%20was%20directly%20ordered%20to%20stop%20investigating%20Trump%20and%20his%20circle%2C%20that%20his%20best%20sources%20were%20closed%20down%2C%20and%20that%20he%20was%20transferred%20from%20his%20human%20intelligence%20squad%20to%20a%20less%20desirable%20assignment%20doing%20surveillance%2C%20one%20that%20had%20little%20to%20do%20with%20this%20skill-set%20or%20experience.%20In%20February%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20bureau%20offered%20him%20%2414%2C000%20to%20drop%20his%20whistleblower%20complaint%20as%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20proposed%20settlement%20for%20a%20separate%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20complaint%20that%20he%20had%20filed.%20Buma%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20to%20experience%20what%20I%20believe%20to%20be%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20Buma%20told%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3Bcharacter%20assassination%2C%20really.%26quot%3B%20His%20disclosure%20says%20that%20Buma%20doesn't%20know%20why%20he%20was%20treated%20this%20way%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20my%20strong%20suspicion%20is%20that%20one%20or%20more%20of%20my%20sources%20provided%20truthful%2C%20accurate%20information%20that%20is%20harmful%20to%20a%20person%20or%20persons%20that%20higher%20ups%20in%20the%20Bureau%20are%20trying%20to%20shield.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMattathias%20Schwartz%20is%20chief%20national%20security%20correspondent%20at%20Insider.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20schwartz79%40protonmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-didnt-care-giuliani-compromised-by-kremlin-whistleblower-buma-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694862061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65049cd2956dba001aceb466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-didnt-care-giuliani-compromised-by-kremlin-whistleblower-buma-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Much%20of%20what%20we%20knew%20about%20Giuliani%2C%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20Burisma%2C%20and%20the%20FBI%20is%20wrong%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20FBI%20whistleblower%20Johnathan%20Buma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mschwartz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mattathias%20Schwartz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A230%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-didnt-care-giuliani-compromised-by-kremlin-whistleblower-buma-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Fran%C3%A7oise%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20woman%2C%20who's%20worth%20%2487%20billion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Francoise%20Bettencourt-Meyers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f1d09e57bff700194845da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFran%C3%A7oise%20Bettencourt-Meyers.%3Cp%3EMartin%20Bureau%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFran%C3%A7oise%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%20inherited%20a%20one-third%20stake%20in%20L'Oreal%20from%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20had%20a%20fraught%20relationship%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20even%20filing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floreal-heire