20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%2015%2C%20citing%20data%20from%20the%20commerce%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20daily%20added%20that%20the%20government%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20optimism%2C%20saying%20that%20exports%20were%20%E2%80%9Cstabilising%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgreenshoots%E2%80%9D%20were%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20merchandise%20trade%20deficit%2C%20or%20the%20gap%20between%20exports%20and%20imports%2C%20reached%20a%2010-month%20high%20of%20%2424.16%20billion%20in%20August.%20This%20was%20driven%20by%20higher%20crude%20oil%20prices%20and%20robust%20domestic%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20almost%2011%25%20jump%20in%20imports%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImports%20were%20recorded%20at%20%2458.64%20billion%20last%20month%2C%20down%205.2%25%20year-on-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20commerce%20secretary%20Sunil%20Barthwal%20attributed%20some%20of%20the%20contraction%20to%20a%20high%20base%20from%20the%20previous%20year%20and%20falling%20commodity%20prices%20affecting%20export%20values%2C%20although%20export%20volumes%20remained%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPessimism%20is%20turning%20into%20optimism%20now%20as%20greenshoots%20are%20clearly%20visible.%20The%20industry%20said%20their%20export%20orders%20were%20better%20and%20they%20were%20also%20optimistic%20about%20export%20order%20books.%20This%20month%20(in%20August)%2C%20at%20least%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20(July%E2%80%99s)%20story%20is%20repeating.%20This%20means%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20improvement%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20global%20exports%20scenario%2C%E2%80%9D%20Barthwal%20said%20in%20a%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fgoods-exports-decline-68-in-august-to-3448-billion-but-green-shoots-visible%2Farticle67312