ssion%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20ruled%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98split%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pawar%20Senior%E2%80%99s%20faction%20has%20thus%20far%20been%20maintaining%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20the%20party%2C%20expressing%20confidence%20that%20the%20poll%20body%20would%20rule%20in%20its%20favour.%20Both%20Sharad%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20factions%20have%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20ECI%20to%20present%20their%20claims%20before%20it%20on%20October%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20up%20by%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20the%20Ajit%20faction%20is%20further%20hopeful%20that%20it%20will%20eventually%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI%20has%20summoned%20both%20factions%20to%20present%20their%20respective%20cases.%20Each%20will%20have%20to%20present%20their%20stance%20on%20why%20they%20have%20the%20right%20over%20the%20party.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20powers%20to%20the%20ECI%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20claim%20to%20the%20party%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20split.%20They%20will%20make%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20after%20hearing%20both%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Pune%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%2016%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fafter-ec-determines-split-in-ncp-ajit-pawar-confident-commission-will-give-appropriate-verdict%2Farticle67312384.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20is%20not%20in%20%E2%80%9Caccordance%20with%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20informed%20the%20ECI%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20NCP.%20But%20without%20hearing%20our%20side%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20decided%20and%20accepted%20the%20split%20in%20NCP.%20We%20are%20seeking%20a%20legal%20opinion%20over%20the%20arbitrary%20decision%20of%20ECI.%20It%20shows%20that%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20ECI%20is%20not%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%20That%20is%20quite%20surprising%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20NCP%20chief%20Jayant%20Patil%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F16%2Fncp-civil-war-sharad-pawar-says-no-split-within-party-ec-refuses-to-accept-it-2615369.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20factions%20have%20been%20vying%20with%20each%20other%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20the%20party%20and%20its%20symbol%20since%20Ajit%E2%80%99s%20faction%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20party%20on%20July%202%20this%20year%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Rebelling%20against%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Ajit%20walked%20out%20with%20eight%20other%20NCP%20leaders%2C%20who%20were%20immediately%20sworn%20in%20as%20ministers%20in%20the%20Shinde%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pawar%20Senior%20faction%2C%20in%20response%2C%20moved%20a%20disqualification%20notice%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20speaker%20seeking%20the%20disqualification%20of%20the%20MLAs%20who%20rebelled%20against%20the%20party.%20The%20matter%20is%20still%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20rebellion%2C%20the%2082-year-old%20NCP%20patriarch%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20been%20travelling%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20holding%20rallies%2C%20underlining%20that%20%E2%80%9Conly%20a%20few%20leaders%20had%20parted%20ways%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20party%20is%20still%20very%20much%20under%20his%20control.%20He%20has%20been%20appealing%20to%20the%20cadre%20to%20encourage%20youngsters%20to%20join%20the%20party%20to%20replace%20the%20leaders%20who%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694855734000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10164456%2FUntitled-design-2-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freal-ncp-