20mix%20of%20colleagues%20from%20work%2C%20and%20complete%20strangers%2C%20was%20jarring%20to%20begin%20with.%20At%20the%20first%20few%20instances%20of%20watching%20prolonged%20scenes%20of%20physical%20intimacy%20in%20close%20quarters%2C%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20and%20froze%20in%20my%20seat.%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20overcome%20the%20internalised%20self-consciousness%20of%20being%20discovered%20I%20feel%20while%20watching%20sexual%20media%20in%20private.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20the%20slow%20trust%20I%20offered%20the%20space%2C%20I%20witnessed%20its%20unabashed%20capacity%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20discussions%20that%20followed%20the%20films.%C2%A0%20Here%2C%20visual%20erotica%20found%20a%20unique%20purpose%2C%20of%20vulnerability%2C%20introspection%2C%20and%20community-building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpectators%20shared%20that%20the%20consumption%20of%20pornography%2C%20and%20its%20utility%2C%20usually%20encourages%20one%20to%20consume%20large%20amounts%20of%20content%2C%20at%20a%20quickened%20pace%2C%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20suitable%20array%20of%20images%3B%20for%20a%20rhythmic%20anticipation%20towards%20orgasm.%20Here%2C%20whereas%20the%20sensuality%20of%20erotica%20remained%2C%20the%20deliberate%20turning%20on%20of%20lights%2C%20demanded%20an%20inversion%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20interior%20self%20to%20this%20public.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%20a%20plethora%20of%20experimental%2C%20documentary%2C%20and%20educational%20films%2C%20peaked%20my%20unwavering%20attention%2C%20during%20some%20screenings%2C%20my%20mind%20wandered%20away%2C%20distracted.%20Regardless%20of%20my%20state%20while%20watching%20these%20films%2C%20they%20demanded%20witnessing%2C%20at%20their%20own%20pace%2C%20on%20their%20own%20terms.%20I%20thought%2C%20for%20a%20space%20built%20around%20kink%2C%20this%20was%20the%20ultimate%20exercise%20in%20submission.%20My%20back%20ached%2C%20my%20throat%20became%20dry%2C%20but%20I%20sat%2C%20every%20day%2C%20for%20three%20days%20on%20my%20seat%2C%20watching.%20For%20extended%20periods%2C%20when%20my%20gaze%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20I%20learnt%20to%20remind%20myself%20to%20let%20loose%2C%20breathe%2C%20shift%20my%20posture%2C%20crack%20my%20back%20and%20take%20a%20sip%20of%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20someone%20like%20myself%2C%20an%20amateur%20kinkster%2C%20films%20offered%20surprising%20moments%20of%20arousal%2C%20in%20sharing%20a%20breadth%20of%20sexual%20acts%20and%20relationships%20that%20minimised%20normative%2C%20peno-vaginal%20sex.%20Vignettes%20of%20tenderness%20in%20these%20relationships%20felt%20like%20warm%20invitations%20that%20made%20me%20intermittently%20message%20my%20partner%20about%20all%20the%20exciting%20possibilities%20of%20sexual%20and%20romantic%20expression%20we%20could%20weave%20into%20our%20lives.%20In%20the%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCu32DWlSAan%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBreathtaking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Morgana%20Muses)%2C%20a%20couple%20indulged%20in%20tender%20breathplay%2C%20where%20the%20dominatrix%20led%20the%20submissive%20to%20luxuriate%20in%20their%20attentive%20care.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESpellbound%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20Ulrike%20Kaffei)%20a%20couple%2C%20crouching%20like%20tigers%2C%20dressed%20in%20black%2C%20tattooed%20extensively%2C%20found%20themselves%20involved%20in%20a%20choreography%20of%20rope-play.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dominatrix%20entangled%20their%20submissive%20in%20an%20intricate%20spider-web%20of%20bright%20red%20rope%2C%20a%20hypnotic%20sight.%20The%20rope%20that%20suspended%20and%20rendered%20the%20submissive%20immobile%2C%20transformed%20into%20a%20blanket%20to%20engulf%20the%20two%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20emotive%20aftercare.%20In%20the%20curiosity%20of%20playing%20with%20breath%20and%20ropes%2C%20I%20wondered%20about%20my%20own%20anxieties%20surrounding%20claustrophobia%20and%20constriction.%20After%20a%20panicked%20experience%20of%20breathlessness%20during%20a%20diving%20trip%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20trust%20I%20instilled%20in%20my%20partner%20who%20held%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20slowly%20led%20me%20into%20the%20ocean%20again.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20float%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20first%20with%20the%20support%20of%20his%20arms%2C%20and%20then%2C%20by%20breathing%20deeply%20with%20the%20ocean%E2%80%99s%20waves%20slowly%20lapping%20me%20up%20in%20a%20rhythmic%20trance.%20Watching%20the%20transcendent%20submissives%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20my%20own%20reintroduction%20to%20the%20ocean%2C%20where%20I%20allowed%20myself%20to%20overcome%20fear%20and%20enter%20a%20meditative%20state%20by%20trusting%20my%20partner%20and%20the%20expansive%20capacity%20of%20my%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20397px)%2085vw%2C%20397px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM.png%20846w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM-212x300.png%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM-722x1024.png%20722w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673257%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Mes%20Amours%2C%20directed%20by%20Anoushka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20catharsis%20in%20these%20films%2C%20I%20felt%20sheer%20joy%20in%20expressions%20of%20queer%20love%2C%20of%20diverse%20bodies%20moving%2C%20shaking%2C%20thumping%20against%20one%20another.%20Some%20in%20the%20audience%20shared%20an%20ache%20and%20longing%20for%20such%20spaces%20of%20celebration%2C%20while%20others%20felt%20emboldened%20to%20imagine%20utopian%20futures%20replete%20with%20joyous%20promise.%20While%20watching%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Debauchary%20Ball%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20David%20Weathersby)%20on%20Chicago%E2%80%99s%20annual%20underground%20ceremony%20of%20Black%20kinky%20sexuality%20and%20House%20music%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20moving%20in%20my%20seat%20to%20the%20electrifying%20beats.%20The%20juxtaposition%20and%20multi-sensorial%20joy%20of%20music%20matching%20the%20colour%20and%20candour%20of%20gyrating%20bodies%2C%20was%20also%20captivating%20in%20the%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVivante%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Anoushka).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20films%20shared%20the%20laughter%2C%20chaos%2C%20and%20the%20frolic%20that%20sex%20truly%20reveals%2C%20in%20between%20positions%20and%20moments%20of%20seduction%20and%20pursuit.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Weekend%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Jan%20Soldat)%2C%20two%20men%20in%20their%2070s%2C%20live%20a%20relaxed%20life%20of%20kink%2C%20where%20naps%20in%20their%20garden%20are%20followed%20by%20a%20play%20of%20flogging%2C%20spanking%20and%20video-archiving%20their%20sexual%20encounters.%20The%20two%20cajole%20each%20other%20like%20high-school%20boys%2C%20tugging%20on%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20bodies%2C%20teasing%20each%20other%20through%20their%20day.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMILF%20Next%20Door%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Sadie%20Lune)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Garage%20My%20Rules%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Manon%20Praline)%2C%20the%20plot%20invoked%20the%20classic%20trope%20of%20porn%20films%2C%20where%20a%20sexual%20encounter%20between%20two%20individuals%20is%20facilitated%20through%20a%20false%20pretext%3B%20a%20jar%20of%20sugar%20from%20the%20next-door%20neighbour%2C%20a%20broken%20car%20awaiting%20repair%20at%20a%20garage.%20Both%20these%20tongue-in-cheek%20premises%20were%20however%2C%20inverted%20in%20the%20films%20with%20a%20non-normative%20cast%20and%20moments%20of%20unpretentious%2C%20unrehearsed%20respite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20ecstasy%20of%20watching%20these%20films%2C%20it%20was%20sobering%20to%20ponder%20on%20the%20discomforts%20of%20kink%3B%20the%20ambiguities%20around%20relationships%2C%20and%20the%20messiness%20it%20entails%2C%20when%20gone%20awry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Least%20I%E2%80%99ve%20Been%20Outside%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20Jan%20Soldat)%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20shares%20a%20comedic%20screen%20recording%20of%20persons%20on%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20rejecting%20his%20request%20of%20filming%20them%20solo.%20A%20jilted%20lover%2C%20navigates%20marriage%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESaint%20and%20Whore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Anne%20Berchad)%20through%20sacrifice%20and%20endurance%2C%20but%20confronts%20and%20wreaks%20havoc%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHouse%20for%20Sale%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Eisha%20Marjara).%20In%20these%20films%2C%20complex%20intersections%20of%20gender%2C%20power%2C%20and%20consent%20provided%20fascinating%20conversation%20among%20the%20attendees%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20contradictory%20thoughts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20two%20occasions%2C%20kink%20educator%20Ancilla%20facilitated%20classes%20on%20Erotic%20Expressionism%20and%20Erotic%20Communication%2C%20creating%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20sex%20education%20class%2C%20I%20had%20not%20received%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20needed.%20The%20introspective%20questions%20in%20the%20seminar%20provoked%20me%20to%20think%20about%20the%20formative%20interiors%20of%20my%20erotic%20self%2C%20and%20brought%20to%20my%20consciousness%20memories%20and%20glimmers%20of%20sensuality%20from%20the%20past.%20In%20sharing%20experiences%20of%20the%20self%20with%20the%20cohort%2C%20instances%20of%20fondness%2C%20betrayal%2C%20the%20complicity%20of%20the%20self%2C%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%20The%20reflexivity%20of%20the%20attendees%20offered%20an%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20what%20felt%20like%20group%20therapy%2C%20akin%20to%20anonymous%20support%20groups%20that%20I%20have%20observed%20in%20films%20and%20television%20before.%20The%20classes%20offered%20thought%20into%20non-genital%2C%20non-sexual%20eroticism%2C%20such%20as%20the%20sartorial%20choices%20of%20sexual%20aestheticism.%20I%20thought%20about%20my%20love%20for%20the%20sari%2C%20a%20garment%20held%20together%20by%20the%20constriction%20of%20the%20petticoat%2C%20whose%20tight%20knot%20around%20my%20waist%20stimulates%2C%20and%20relieves%2C%20with%20its%20untying%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20location%20of%20the%20festival%20at%20Akshara%20Theatre%20in%20Delhi%20amused%20me.%20The%20venue%20has%20been%20a%20site%20of%20cultural%20memory%2C%20where%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20plays%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20which%20now%20carries%20a%20re-inscribed%20meaning.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98edge%2C%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20made%20me%20think%20about%20%E2%80%98edging%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20the%20prolonged%20restraining%20of%20climax%2C%20which%20truly%20was%20the%20experience%20of%20watching%20these%20films.%20In%20the%20safety%20and%20warmth%20of%20a%20community%2C%20a%20dark%20theatre%20transformed%20into%20a%20space%20for%20vulnerability%2C%20openness%2C%20and%20sharing%2C%20morning%20to%20evening%20for%20three%20day