%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20became%20a%20government%20school%20teacher%20when%20I%20was%2019.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20do%20my%20graduation%20then%20as%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20teaching%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20could.%20All%20I%20did%20was%20complete%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20training%20programme%20and%20appear%20for%20its%20qualifying%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20Archana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%205%20September%202023%2C%20she%20received%20the%20National%20Teachers%20Award%20from%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20at%20the%20Vigyan%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20These%20awards%20are%20conferred%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20to%20the%20finest%20school%20teachers%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20improved%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20and%20brought%20about%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20students.%20This%20award%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20her%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20towards%20the%20teaching%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20headmistress%20first%20started%20as%20a%20primary%20school%20class%20teacher%20here%20in%20Telangana.%20From%20a%20non-descript%20centre%20of%20learning%20with%20just%20a%20few%20students%2C%20this%20educator%20has%20transformed%20the%20school%20into%20a%20mecca%20of%20learning%2C%20offering%20holistic%20growth%20through%20a%20variety%20of%20extra-curricular%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20change%20were%20sown%20in%20Archana%E2%80%99s%20mind%20at%20home.%20She%20saw%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20serve%20students.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20would%20teach%20a%20lot%20of%20tribal%20students.%20He%20used%20to%20teach%20them%20at%20our%20house%20and%20helped%20them%20in%20their%20higher%20studies.%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20like%20him%20and%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWh