9%2Famerican-english-teacher-elizabeth-keyton-started-elikutty-to-learn-and-teach-malayalam-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etireless%20efforts%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20ensure%20that%20the%20tribal%20students%20in%20the%20village%20are%20educated%2C%20she%20has%20increased%20the%20strength%20to%20275%20students%20today%2C%20with%20103%20being%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20she%20also%20worked%20on%20developing%20the%20school%20infrastructure.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20a%20former%20student%20of%20her%20school%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20abroad.%20NGOs%20like%20Bring%20a%20Smile%20Foundation%2C%20Padmavati%20Charitable%20Trust%20and%20local%20politicians%20also%20joined%20hands%20to%20support%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20able%20to%20procure%20a%20borewell%2C%20purified%20water%20plant%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20built%20a%20beautiful%20library%20with%201000%20books%2C%20through%20their%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajendra%20has%20helped%20tremendously%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20school.%20He%20is%20the%20person%20through%20whom%20we%20got%20most%20of%20the%20donations.%20The%20Washington%20Telangana%20Association%20(WATA)%20helped%20us%20get%2040%20benches%20for%20the%20school%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20A%20local%20MLA%20installed%20the%20borewell%20and%20an%20RO%20plant%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20learning%20more%20fun%2C%20through%20digital%20technology%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20(ICT)%20initiative%2C%20she%20procured%20five%20computers%2C%20two%20LED%20projectors%20and%20two%20additional%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICT%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20School%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202004%20to%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20secondary%20stage%20students%20to%20mainly%20bu