ould%20benefit%20you%20too.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Laxmi%20Sri%20Pandrala%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20from%20Bengaluru%20launched%20her%20healthcare%20venture%20Lami.fit%20in%20the%20year%202019%2C%20she%20was%20certain%20it%20was%20a%20step%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20way%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20was%20perceived%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20Citing%20the%20reasons%20behind%20this%20thought%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20shocking%20revelation%20I%20came%20across%20during%20my%20practice%20is%20that%20one%20in%20four%20Indians%20die%20of%20NCDs%20(non-communicable%20diseases)%2C%20while%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20these%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20prevented%20were%20the%20condition%20detected%20in%20time.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%20changes%20in%20lifestyle%2C%20she%20notes%2C%20could%20bring%20about%20a%20reversal%20of%20the%20condition.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20years%20Laxmi%20spent%20consulting%20at%20a%20hospital%20following%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20nutrition%2C%20she%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20tackle%20this%20gap%2C%20Laxmi%20started%20her%20venture%20Lami.fit%20based%20upon%20the%20solid%20idea%20that%20good%20health%20was%20within%20reach%20if%20the%20right%20approach%20was%20followed.%20As%20she%20explains%2C%20at%20the%20health%20optimisation%20platform%2C%20a%20full%20workup%20of%20the%20patient%20is%20coupled%20with%20blood%20tests%2C%20followed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3