n%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20memories%20of%20their%20early%20years%20are%20woven%20into%20every%20brick%20and%20corner%20that%20my%20husband%20assembled%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rupa%20Bai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Jyoti%20has%20enjoyed%20Rupa%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20company%20among%20the%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeautiful%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20cemented.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20take%20things%20as%20they%20come.%20Everything%20happens%20in%20its%20own%20space%20and%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devra%20prides%20itself%20on%20traditional%20Udaipur%20culture%20and%20authentic%20delicacies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-150x100.jpg%2